<h2><span class=3D"header-section-number">1.19</span> Binary dependent
variable: 2-by-2 vrequency table with pretest data</h2>
<p>This method approximates Cohen=E2=80=99s <span class=3D"math inline"><sp=
an class=3D"MathJax_Preview" style=3D"color: inherit;"><span class=3D"MJXp-=
math" id=3D"MJXp-Span-2974"><span class=3D"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id=3D"MJXp-=
