MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id=3D"MJXp-Span-3715">g</span></span></span></span>. T=
he method determines the phi
coefficient associated with the <span class=3D"math inline"><span class=3D"=
MathJax_Preview" style=3D"color: inherit;"><span class=3D"MJXp-math" id=3D"=
MJXp-Span-3716"><span class=3D"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id=3D"MJXp-Span-3717">p=
</span></span></span></span>
value and by first determining the <span class=3D"math inline"><span class=
