<h1><span class=3D"header-section-number">2</span> The Odds Ratio and Risk
Ratio</h1>
<p>The odds ratio and risk ratio are suitable for meta-analyses where
both the independent variable and the dependent variable are binary. In
the case of a non-dichotomous dependent variable, the odds ratio (but
not the risk ratio) can be approximated by first computing Cohen=E2=80=99s =
