<div id=3D"odds-ratio-and-risk-ratio-from-percents" class=3D"section level2=
" number=3D"2.3">
<h2><span class=3D"header-section-number">2.3</span> Odds ratio and risk
ratio from percents</h2>
<p>Recall that percents are simply proportions multiplied by 100. Thus,
this method converts percents (with a range between 0 and 100,
inclusively) into percents (with a range between 0 and 10, inclusively)
by dividing by 100. The method of computing the odds and risk ratios
from proportions is then used.</p>
</div>
